{"tid":848132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［PlanB開腔回應］李卓人：當年我支持修改議事規則與議會抗爭無直接關係！","createTime":"2018-10-04T16:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T01:23:54.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"79b2fcdac4d197f94fde5255e74844a2ea568fec","tid":848132,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:34:15.000Z","msg":"修改議事規則一役李卓人被屌足7年，泛民一直臭屎密琴，今日李卓人因九西planB被屌忽然開腔回應當年一事！<br />\n<br />\n2011年泛民支持收緊議事規則，將主席驅逐議員離場權力擴展到各事務委員會<br />\n<br />\n李卓人9月27日為了planB被屌而回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9OfFoq8og8Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9OfFoq8og8Q&d=v5Iz2pQ3lg%2BbtHTvfN070TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3d999197\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9OfFoq8og8Q</a><br />\n19:29 開始<br />\n<br />\n李卓人：<br />\n事務委員會不是財委員及大會等，我哋覺得事務委員會係傾政策野，我哋唔想係傾政策野時因為某啲情況而斷咗個會議搞到冇得傾落去，因為斷咗個會就可以直接上財委會，財委會才是要抗爭要守嘅地方。事務委員會冇咩需要守，財委會嗰啲就要用到議事規則去守，所以我哋先會係財委會駁命入修訂。<br />\n<br />\n若用寸土必爭角度去睇，我俾人趕出場嗰陣有幾多人同我一樣？議會入邊俾人趕出場趕得最多肯定有我份！<br />\n（鄭宇碩：馮檢基反而冇俾人趕出場喎～）<br />\n所以成個議事規則修改係同抗爭冇一個直接關係，事務委員會只係講人力事務職安健等等..."},{"pid":"f2d196c17fcd5c04198aa8d78668f6d8355be23c","tid":848132,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14b274525dd2afbe7ad9e1fc83c82f5bf70c4a1","tid":848132,"uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:44:01.000Z","msg":"李卓人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 李卓人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kk39dBGPAt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dkk39dBGPAt4&d=v5Iz2pQ3lg%2BbtHTvfN070TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1178c89a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kk39dBGPAt4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7572209b2455ca4b86f76a96fac4072a7959dc1","tid":848132,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"講到尾咪又係想打壓異己"},{"pid":"761e1efca2cb1b1df4cfbb14f3ab290193186dd6","tid":848132,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92362554653689da9936835ffc70cb590c614416","tid":848132,"uid":47198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T17:24:46.000Z","msg":"佢地終將受到歷史嘅懲罰！<br />\n<br />\n屌你即刻彈返毓民呢句出黎"},{"pid":"41c5d5d24fbe565a6dfe21aa737eac064ab0c72e","tid":848132,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eada4d1817b090412ff18619814bd0f96683648","tid":848132,"uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T17:27:34.000Z","msg":"Sze Tat Chau<br />\n2小時 &middot; <br />\n毓民：「如果你（李卓人）呢個撚樣去選，我就一定開街站架！我就動員返，喂，閒閒地開四五十個街站架喇真係！」全力支持！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fb35549e1f142f4505e1232dbd8235691adfbc","tid":848132,"uid":49388,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">（鄭宇碩：馮檢基反而冇俾人趕出場喎～）</span><br />\n<br />\nTo: 鄭宇碩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bLcEUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bLcEUh.jpg&h=366c69f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"p